title: MisterMusic Show 352 - indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show #352  - 2 hours   192kbps MP3


On The MisterMusic Show this week, New indie rock from Pony The Pirate, Robyn Sherwell, Mother Mother, and Lowly.
Plus one of the 500 greatest rock songs of all-time is the 'Oldie of the Week'. 
A song that was number 1 the first week of May 1977.

It's over 5 decades of indie, alternative and rock hits-The MisterMusic Show.

The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
